rtion of flesh,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of hard flesh,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baATin", "text_ar": "بَاطِن"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sole,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "inner part,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the solid hoof,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "as though it were a pebble,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a date-stone,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what rises in the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bATn", "text_ar": "باطن"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the hoof of the horse, from,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of, the upper part thereof:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K:) or the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bATn", "text_ar": "باطن"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "itself of the solid hoof:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nusuwrN", "text_ar": "نُسُورٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (M, K,) which Aboo-Sa'eed explains as signifying the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "prominences in the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baTon", "text_ar": "بَطْن"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sole"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the solid hoof, which are likened to date-stones because of their hardness, and which do not touch the ground."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) Hence the saying,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaAfirN Sulobu", "text_ar": "حَافِرٌ صُلْبُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aln~usuwri", "text_ar": "النُّسُورِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A solid hoof hard in the frog:"}, {"kind": "text", "text"